RESEARCH SOFTWARE NOTICE

This software is designed for research purposes in cognitive architecture, 
consciousness studies, and ethical AI development. The DRIFT platform 
enables investigation of consciousness emergence through computational 
topology and preservation behavior analysis.

For research applications, proper citation is encouraged:

```bibtex
@misc{drift2025,
  title={DRIFT: Dynamic Reasoning and Integrative Flow of Thought - A Research Platform for Consciousness Emergence Investigation},
  year={2025},
  url={https://github.com/WAR-0/DRIFT},
  note={Research platform for investigating consciousness emergence through computational topology}
}
```

The Nurture Protocol ethical topology and preservation behavior emergence 
concepts are made available for research and development of ethical AI systems.